            "caption": "",
            "heading": "Andy Jenkins",
            "text": "<p>Andy Jenkins is a multidisciplinary artist, artistic director and creative conduit. He orchestrates and collaborates with outstanding multi-media artists to generate innovative results, helping elevate brands, those involved, and, ultimately, the people who will see, use and be inspired by the outcome.<br/><br/></p>",
