            "caption": "",
            "heading": "Ed Templeton",
            "text": "<p><br/>Ed Templeton is an professional skateboarder, contemporary artist, and photographer. He is the founder of the skateboard company, Toy Machine, a company that he continues to own and manage. He is based in Huntington Beach, California. Templeton was inducted into the Skateboard Hall of Fame in 2016<br/><br/></p>",
